elements.name: Adding language to an Employee by Language,Fluency & Competency

embeddings.name: Adding language to an Employee by Language,Fluency & Competency

steps.name: user is logged in HRMS with valid Admin Credential
user is naviaged to Employee information page and click on an "9669A"
User is navigated to add Language window
User selects a language named "English"
user selects "Writing" and "Good" from DataTable for "English"
User Verifies that "English" is added with "Writing" and "Good"
